  "text": "### Scenario 4: Poor Customer Service  \n**Your Issue:** \"Staff member was rude to me in the branch.\"  \n**What We Investigate:**\n- When did this occur?\n- Who was the staff member?\n- What was said/done?\n- How did it impact you?  \n**Possible Outcomes:**\n- **Service failure confirmed:** Apology; staff retraining; compensation (£20–£100 depending on severity)\n- **Misunderstanding:** Explanation of staff's actions; clarification\n- **Not substantiated:** Explanation of our findings  \n**Typical Resolution Time:** 5–7 business days  \n---",
